1062
00:50:26,430 --> 00:50:30,550
I think we'll get a little more than 10.

1063
00:50:30,550 --> 00:50:34,440
It's higher in quality than our last work.

1064
00:50:34,440 --> 00:50:36,480
We did fast-paced editing, too.

1065
00:50:36,480 --> 00:50:39,460
I don't think there are boring moments.

1066
