Try to be punctual.

1081
00:51:19,270 --> 00:51:20,700
You're always late. It's too much.

1082
00:51:20,750 --> 00:51:23,850
You think five hours is nothing?
You're seriously ridicule.

1083
00:51:23,850 --> 00:51:26,050
- You mean "ridiculous," idiot.
- Good for you, asshole.

1084
00:51:26,090 --> 00:51:27,300
You're seriously ridicule.

1085
