1092
00:51:47,800 --> 00:51:50,910
I wasn't hearing laughter when I planned it.

1093
00:51:50,910 --> 00:51:53,140
I was so embarrassed.

1094
00:51:54,240 --> 00:51:55,960
I told you not to argue about everything.

1095
00:51:55,960 --> 00:51:58,360
Look at him, Jeong Hun.

1096
00:51:58,360 --> 00:52:02,070
Grandma, I have friends now.

1097
00:52:02,070 --> 00:52:04,320
