1108
00:52:27,890 --> 00:52:29,140
I need to feed Myung Soo.

1109
00:52:29,140 --> 00:52:30,700
Who's Myung Soo? Why do you have to feed him?

1110
00:52:30,700 --> 00:52:32,360
His father's name is Myung Soo.

1111
00:52:32,360 --> 00:52:33,760
My dad is Byung Soo.

1112
00:52:33,760 --> 00:52:36,360
Myung Soo is my little brother.

1113
00:52:36,360 --> 00:52:37,960
[Why won't they laugh?]

1114
00:52:37,960 --> 00:52:40,070
Myung Soo is my little brother.

1115
00:52:40,070 --> 00:52:42,650
[The impenetrable audience]

1116
00:52:42,650 --> 00:52:43,920
My place is this way.

1117
00:52:43,950 --> 00:52:47,530
The dog is so cute.
Why don't people find him cute?

1118
00:52:47,530 --> 00:52:49,540
My Morae is a cute dog.

1119
00:52:49,540 --> 00:52:52,370
