- Excuse me.

1123
00:52:59,750 --> 00:53:03,620
Myung Soo, bark when someone's home.

1124
00:53:03,620 --> 00:53:05,830
Come here. Check out my room.

1125
00:53:10,440 --> 00:53:12,570
What are you doing, Jeong Hun?

1126
