1129
00:53:25,300 --> 00:53:29,110
[The stop count stopped]

1130
00:53:34,750 --> 00:53:37,830
Shit, nothing f***ing works.

1131
00:53:48,060 --> 00:53:49,290
[After School]

1132
00:53:50,010 --> 00:53:53,320
["After School" ends with a strong impression]

1133
00:53:53,740 --> 00:53:55,640
I like the ending.

1134
00:53:56,530 --> 00:53:59,790
- I wish we had seen that sooner.
- Yes! Really.

1135
00:54:00,710 --> 00:54:05,070
I wish the murder scene had
happened a little sooner.

1136
00:54:05,070 --> 00:54:06,840
They should've given up on jokes.

1137
00:54:06,840 --> 00:54:09,640
I didn't find those jokes funny.

1138
00:54:09,640 --> 00:54:13,820
