1140
00:54:15,600 --> 00:54:19,650
The total stop count is 24.

1141
00:54:19,650 --> 00:54:22,260
What did you think?
Are you happy with the result?

1142
00:54:22,260 --> 00:54:24,620
I expected something more like 10.

1143
00:54:24,620 --> 00:54:26,880
I'm upset that we got a lot more.

1144
00:54:26,880 --> 00:54:29,720
[So cute]

1145
00:54:29,720 --> 00:54:31,540
What do we do?

1146
00:54:32,240 --> 00:54:34,500
[Hae On is upset]

1147
00:54:34,500 --> 00:54:37,130
We watched three short dramas so far.

1148
00:54:37,130 --> 00:54:38,760
I had a moment of weakness each time.

1149
00:54:38,760 --> 00:54:41,500
- My hand kept going here.
- Push or not push?

1150
00:54:41,500 --> 00:54:43,740
This is how short dramas are.

1151
00:54:43,740 --> 00:54:45,330
When did you have that moment?

1152
00:54:45,330 --> 00:54:47,820
It was when they talked about Myung Soo.

1153
00:54:47,820 --> 00:54:50,060
The number went up a lot then.

1154
00:54:50,060 --> 00:54:51,440
I need to feed Myung Soo.

1155
00:54:51,440 --> 00:54:53,010
Who's Myung Soo? Why do you have to feed him?

1156
00:54:53,010 --> 00:54:54,480
His father's name is Myung Soo.

1157
00:54:54,480 --> 00:54:56,170
My dad is Byung Soo.

1158
00:54:56,170 --> 00:54:57,660
Myung Soo is my little brother.

1159
00:54:57,660 --> 00:54:59,070
I thought it was funny.

1160
00:54:59,070 --> 00:55:01,620
- The dog?
- It was moving fast before,

1161
00:55:01,620 --> 00:55:05,920
