1162
00:55:05,950 --> 00:55:09,650
I almost pressed the button then,
but it was recovered well.

1163
00:55:09,700 --> 00:55:11,770
We saw Shin Ki.

1164
00:55:11,770 --> 00:55:13,530
Right, Shin Ki.

1165
00:55:13,530 --> 00:55:14,720
I know.

1166
00:55:14,720 --> 00:55:16,880
That grabbed my attention.

1167
00:55:16,880 --> 00:55:19,260
I ended up not pressing until the end.

1168
00:55:19,260 --> 00:55:21,720
I think he only pressed it for ours.

1169
00:55:21,750 --> 00:55:24,650
- I know.
- He only pressed for ours.

1170
00:55:24,700 --> 00:55:26,970
Do you know Lee Shin Ki?

1171
00:55:26,970 --> 00:55:29,000
