I got to work with him through a friend.

1174
00:55:37,420 --> 00:55:41,620
That's how we met, and we've been in touch since.

1175
00:55:41,620 --> 00:55:44,080
He played an important part today.

1176
00:55:44,080 --> 00:55:49,740
Is this something unique to Director's Arena?

1177
00:55:49,740 --> 00:55:53,130
In other competition shows,

1178
