1179
00:55:58,280 --> 00:56:01,110
But we're auditioning directors.

1180
00:56:01,110 --> 00:56:06,670
Their connections can be very helpful, too.

1181
00:56:06,670 --> 00:56:13,560
I think Shin Ki helped
this short drama immensely.

1182
00:56:13,560 --> 00:56:17,950
Okay, then. Team "After School" got 24 stops.

1183
00:56:17,950 --> 00:56:22,050
But how long was their average viewing time?

1184
00:56:22,050 --> 00:56:26,130
