Please reveal.

1192
00:56:42,990 --> 00:56:45,000
[Everyone is focused]

1193
00:56:51,840 --> 00:56:54,430
86.83 seconds.

1194
00:56:54,430 --> 00:56:55,900
Second place. Second place.

1195
00:56:55,900 --> 00:56:58,000
[Team "After School" is
currently in second place]

