00:56:58,000 --> 00:57:00,320
It's so close. 81, 86.

1197
00:57:00,320 --> 00:57:04,260
[Team "Taste of Youth" is in third place]

1198
00:57:04,260 --> 00:57:06,530
100 seconds was a lot.

1199
00:57:06,530 --> 00:57:10,950
